would like the americans to play the peace card it sees the war 
card coming up us diplomats predict new military offensives and 
ussupplied rockets pound kabul every day 
the meeting in stockholm sweden will be the first superpower 
discussion focusing on the 10year afghan civil war since the last 
soviet troops left this central asian nation feb 15 
najib has confounded western diplomats who predicted moslem 
rebels would topple his sovietbacked government within days of the 
soviet pullout he remains in power while the guerrillas who call 
themselves mujahedeen or islamic holy warriors appear to be 
squabbling among themselves 
