cambodias future 
however he said washington was willing to support sihanouks 
inclusion of the khmer rouge one of the parties of his loose 
coalition in an interim arrangement he further qualified the 
position by saying the actual khmer rouge leaders responsible for 
the deaths of hundreds of thousands of cambodians could never be 
allowed to return to power 
the strength of our support for any cambodian government 
however will directly and inversely depend on the extent of khmer 
rouge participation if any in that government baker said 
